---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Fini's Kitchens"
  description="Part of the Fini Group. Kitchen design and installation born from love, loss, and a commitment to make dreams come true."
  eyebrow="Who we are"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-head">
        <div class="section-head__copy">
          <h2 class="section-head__title">Part of the Fini Group</h2>
          <p class="section-head__desc">
            We’re part of the wider Fini Group, offering services to support and improve clients’ lives through our
            professional passions: Kitchen Renovations, Cleaning Services & Software.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid--2 about-grid">
        <div class="stack">
          <p class="muted">
            From design to installation, we handle every detail so you can focus on the joy of your new kitchen.
          </p>
          <p class="muted">
            We care about layouts, materials and the little details that make the space feel easy to live in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="media media--1x1 about-media">
          <div class="about-placeholder">Team photo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-head">
        <div class="section-head__copy">
          <h2 class="section-head__title">Fini’s story</h2>
          <p class="section-head__desc">
            The forming idea of Fini’s Kitchens stems from the tragic and sudden loss of our Co-Owners’ 20-month-old son
            Finan “Fini” Wyatt to a very rare condition in January 2024.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid--2 about-grid about-grid--reverse">
        <div class="media media--16x9 about-media">
          <div class="video-placeholder">
            <span class="video-placeholder__play" aria-hidden="true">▶</span>
            <span class="video-placeholder__label">Fini’s Story (Video)</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack">
          <p class="muted">
            Since then we’ve only wanted to use business as a force for good and make dreams come true.
            Every kitchen we design carries his name and spirit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-head">
        <div class="section-head__copy">
          <h2 class="section-head__title">The team</h2>
          <p class="section-head__desc">A small team with a big obsession: kitchens that work beautifully in real life.</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid--3 team-grid">
        <article class="card card--surface team">
          <div class="team__avatar" aria-hidden="true">OW</div>
          <h3>Oli Wyatt</h3>
          <p class="faint team__role">CEO & Designer</p>
          <p class="muted">The Designer</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card card--surface team">
          <div class="team__avatar" aria-hidden="true">VN</div>
          <h3>Viki Nasch</h3>
          <p class="faint team__role">COO</p>
          <p class="muted">The Brains</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card card--surface team">
          <div class="team__avatar" aria-hidden="true">JP</div>
          <h3>Jason Peters</h3>
          <p class="faint team__role">CTO</p>
          <p class="muted">The Magician</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid { margin-top: var(--space-8); align-items: center; }
  .about-grid--reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .about-grid--reverse > * { direction: ltr; }

  .about-media {
    border-radius: var(--radius-l);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
  }

  .about-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--c-text-faint);
    border: 1px dashed var(--c-border-strong);
    background: var(--c-surface-2);
  }

  .video-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--c-text);
    background: var(--c-surface-2);
  }

  .video-placeholder__play {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: #ef4444;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .video-placeholder__label {
    color: var(--c-text-faint);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .team { text-align: center; }
  .team__avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--c-on-accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-accent), var(--c-accent-strong));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .team__role { margin-top: var(--space-2); }
</style>